57.4	Christina_Hendricks	Christina Hendricks	Christina Rene Hendricks (born May 3, 1975) is an English-American actress known for her role as Joan Holloway in the AMC cable television series Mad Men, and as Saffron in Fox's short-lived series Firefly. A poll of female readers taken by Esquire magazine named Hendricks "the sexiest woman in the world."	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6a/Christina_Hendricks_%40_BE_booth.jpg/220px-Christina_Hendricks_%40_BE_booth.jpg
